quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,19,"And the intoxication of death will bring the truth; that is what you were trying to avoid."
  50,20,"And the Horn will be blown. That is the Day of [carrying out] the threat."
  50,21,"And every soul will come, with it a driver and a witness.{1}",footnotes:1:i.e., one angel driving the soul to the Judgement and one to testify as to its deeds.
  51,13,"[It is] the Day they will be tormented over the Fire."
  51,14,"[And will be told], "
  51,15,"Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and springs,"
  52,4,"And [by] the frequented House{1}",footnotes:1:The house of worship for the angels in the seventh heaven, comparable to the Kaʿbah on earth.
  52,5,"And [by] the ceiling [i.e., heaven] raised high"
  52,6,"And [by] the sea set on fire,{1}",footnotes:1:On the Day of Resurrection.  Or "the sea which has overflowed."